00:22:13,291 --> 00:22:15,583
SHE DIDN'T EVEN WATCH
THE BROADCAST.

430
00:22:15,666 --> 00:22:19,458
- SO, KOKO, I MUST SAY,
I REMAIN VERY CURIOUS TO SEE

431
00:22:19,541 --> 00:22:23,708
WHAT IT IS YOU'RE PLOTTING.
CAN I PLEASE BE A PART OF IT?

432
00:22:23,791 --> 00:22:26,916
