NEW LOGISTICS PACKAGE,

436
00:22:36,666 --> 00:22:38,250
THE HEKMATYAR GLOBAL GRID,

437
00:22:38,333 --> 00:22:40,541
WHICH WILL REVOLUTIONIZE
HOW ARMIES ARE SUPPLIED

438
00:22:40,625 --> 00:22:42,875
AND HOW WARS ARE FOUGHT AND WON.

439
00:22:42,958 --> 00:22:45,208
- THAT'S NOT WHAT
I'M TALKING ABOUT, KOKO.

440
00:22:45,291 --> 00:22:48,291
