442
00:22:51,583 --> 00:22:53,958
BUT THAT DOESN'T MEAN
I'M GIVING UP ON THIS.

443
00:22:54,041 --> 00:22:56,625
IF YOU FIND YOU NEED ME
FOR YOUR PROJECT, PLEASE CALL.

444
00:22:56,708 --> 00:22:59,291
- I HAVE NO IDEA WHAT
YOU'RE REFERRING TO.

445
00:22:59,375 --> 00:23:01,041
<i>- DASVIDANIYA</i> FOR NOW.

446
00:23:01,125 --> 00:23:03,291
THANK YOU FOR
YOUR BUSINESS, KOKO.

447
00:23:03,375 --> 00:23:06,541
I'M SURE I'LL BE SEEING
YOU AGAIN SOON.

448
00:23:09,666 --> 00:23:12,958
- THERE I WAS,
TRAVELING WITH AN ARMS DEALER.

449
00:23:13,041 --> 00:23:15,041
LOOKING BACK,

450
00:23:15,125 --> 00:23:18,666
I REALIZE I DIDN'T
UNDERSTAND KOKO AT ALL.

451
00:23:18,750 --> 00:23:21,166
- Koko:
JONAH, LET'S TAKE A WALK.

452
00:23:23,500 --> 00:23:27,250
