00:23:28,458 --> 00:23:30,583
SHE WAS ALWAYS SO CLOSE TO ME,


455
00:23:30,666 --> 00:23:32,750
YET IMPOSSIBLE TO REACH.


456
00:23:32,833 --> 00:23:36,916
